caption: This place is elite. Very tasty food, super friendly and accommodating staff and Chef Kelvin is the man.

This is place is absolutely incredibly. The lamb pita is life changing. We arrived right before closing and Chef Kelvin made us feel right at home and made sure we had the full Miznon experience! My friends and I will be back without a doubt

Chef Kelvin was incredible. Super welcoming, made us feel great, and helped us figure out what we wanted. The music was awesome and just great vibes overall. Highly recommend for a hangout with friends or a date night.
Super-good Israeli food. Great addition to the neighborhood.

From the first bite to the last nibble ( you take smaller bites towards the end because you don't want it to end) every single bite is a firework explosion of flavors. I wish that there was a 6 or 10 star rating option. Real talk, this is the absolute best food I have ever had. And the great energy and enthusiasm for good food and flavors from the kitchen staff is prevalent in thing you order. It's so awesome seeing the chefs have fun making your food, how could it not be amazing. AND ITS (ALL) AMAZING, from the folded burger (oh my lord, the folded burger, yooooo) to the chicken joint and the mushroom pita, oh my sheesh. Oh and don't forget about that steak joint either the candy or the ribeye! Yo when people say food is love... this is the epitome. Please do yourself a favor and go see these guys and fill up. You will be back!!! Believe that.
The food is amazing, but it is already twice in a row that they forget to put drinks with our order. No one answered the phone, when tried to call them both times. 🤷‍♀️ Not happy about that.
Can’t wait to try this one out 🙌🏼 (Oct 3rd 2020)
